185700
185800     IF      ATTRIBUTE RESTARTED OF  MYSELF  EQUAL VALUE TRUE
185900             DISPLAY "PC/GAA/T255/DB  -  FIM NORMAL"
186000             GO      000-S-MONITORA.
186100
