547278*        TRATA A TAXA DE PRECO PUBLICO SE FOR ENCONTRADA         *
547280******************************************************************
547282*
547284 800-E-TAXAS-PP.
547286
547288     SET     TAXPLACASS1             TO      ENDING.
547290     MOVE    2                       TO      AX-TAX-SITU.
547292
547294
547296 800-10-TAXAS-PP.
547298
547300     LOCK    PRIOR   TAXPLACASS1     AT
547302             TAX-SITUACAO            =       AX-TAX-SITU     AND
547304             TAX-PLACA-MERC          =       PLC-PLACA-MERC  AND
547306             TAX-COD-PAG             =       93
547308       ON    EXCEPTION
